      "name": "CFD vs experimental hemolysis index — FDA pump benchmark",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) against in-vitro measurements from the FDA benchmark study across five flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 18.4%; model under-predicts hemolysis at high shear conditions.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4041290"
