      "name": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on hemolysis predictions",
      "description": "10,000-sample Monte Carlo propagation of inlet boundary condition and rheological parameter uncertainties. 95th-percentile NIH prediction interval spans 0.31–0.74 mg/100 L, exceeding the clinical threshold at two operating points.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1016/j.compbiomed.2023.107410"
    }
  ],
